{"tid":2443334,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁美芬、何君堯及數十名律師和大律師參與聯署：支持人大決定「完善」選舉制度","createTime":"2021-03-12T04:11:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T07:07:21.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a0977afff4d611107fc4849e7aed0ea940940857","tid":2443334,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T04:11:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580215-20210312.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580215-20210312.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgwzMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=fc128053\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580215-20210312.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=6d2959b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580215-20210312.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n有法律界人士聯署，全力支持全國人大決定「完善」香港選舉制度。聯署人包括立法會議員梁美芬、何君堯、周浩鼎及容海恩。截至昨晚9時，有數十名律師和大律師參與聯署。<br />\n<br />\n聯署表示，有關決定符合《中英聯合聲明》、《基本法》及「一國兩制」。《憲法》及《基本法》明確指出，中央有權責「完善」香港的選舉制度。<br />\n<br />\n聯署指，香港的選舉制度出現漏洞，以致有當選者在就職宣誓時作出侮辱國家民族的行為；擔任議員後，要求外國制裁香港，又作出癱瘓議會運作等傷害國家及香港利益的行為，這些都嚴重超越「一國兩制」底線。<br />\n<br />\n聯署又指，人大通過的決定能堵塞漏洞，屬高瞻遠矚，消除激進攬炒、破壞等政治亂象。有望解決香港深層次矛盾，令「一國兩制」行得更遠更好。他們相信，「完善」選舉制度後能吸引更多符合愛國者準則的人士加入政府及議會，讓治港的愛國者不局限於建制派政黨政團。"},{"pid":"effcb22afe0dbdc0d252d4b11aa6aa6ecaf11c78","tid":2443334,"uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T04:12:07.000Z","msg":"點解都似係「完結」, 多過「完善」 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"864c416885022071857e2177cbe800889f16edda","tid":2443334,"uid":26224,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T04:19:58.000Z","msg":"想知到邊幾個簽. <br />\n律師簽呢d 野個名實臭"},{"pid":"ca93c2fdab05ffc663ee0f269d73e7b41cac74bb","tid":2443334,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T04:33:12.000Z","msg":"張名單backup定都得"},{"pid":"4b6e83d30f9032bd543e267af497121cac99dca3","tid":2443334,"uid":60238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T04:35:11.000Z","msg":"你班奴才<br />\n主子嘅決定邊撚度需要你&quot;支持&quot;"},{"pid":"08e1eaf0c5cf82b5ea4860a5e5f686b04d4ce68d","tid":2443334,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T04:42:16.000Z","msg":"保皇曱甴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59dfaf8b5eb89232f9a6ce574a3f0a1f3193dd4c","tid":2443334,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T04:42:55.000Z","msg":"奶啦奶啦，好快到你地俾人鬥死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"161f2fc5349cffeb8f9b053225c9781fa1dc121d","tid":2443334,"uid":11719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T04:43:36.000Z","msg":"忠誠廢物"},{"pid":"90f7334b43cb5de5ac247141679b161c090091b1","tid":2443334,"uid":256059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T04:59:03.000Z","msg":"仲有民賤聯班友區區大量擺街站又收集簽名，各方又登報又派傳單洗樓又聯署，支國都決定左，又無佢所謂反對派，點解仲要發動搭呢台戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  (除左拎budget ..)"},{"pid":"5cdadde2af07847e24deec03982dca1eb52980c6","tid":2443334,"uid":375135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T05:01:18.000Z","msg":"退步.......=完結"},{"pid":"d44e1c07e09046ca91d3ade8e891a085babdf27b","tid":2443334,"uid":30067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T07:07:21.000Z","msg":"上年個個話何君堯冇得再做立法會<br />\n而家睇個樣又有得做"}]}